rows.label: qst202301_0010
rows.name:
Yaegiri asked us to meet her
here, but she's not here herself...

rows.label: qst202301_0020
rows.name: Did we get the right time?

rows.label: qst202301_0030
rows.name: Yes, I'm sure of it.

rows.label: qst202301_0040
rows.name: More likely she just oversleep or something.

rows.label: qst202301_0050
rows.name: Good! I made it just in time!

rows.label: qst202301_0060
rows.name: Actually a little bit late.

rows.label: qst202301_0070
rows.name:
Huh? Sorry! Sorry!
Okay, I guess I am late.

rows.label: qst202301_0080
rows.name:
I got a bit sidetracked fighting a
massive monster on the way here.

rows.label: qst202301_0090
rows.name: I must have gotten a bit carried away in the thick of it.

rows.label: qst202301_0100
rows.name: Yaegiri, you're always up for it. I like that.

rows.label: qst202301_0110
rows.name: Haha! You know it.

rows.label: qst202301_0120
rows.name:
So what did you want to
talk to us about, Yaegiri?

rows.label: qst202301_0130
rows.name:
Right!
I wanted to lodge a complaint.

rows.label: qst202301_0140
rows.name:
You all know how much I like fighting
really powerful enemies, right?

rows.label: qst202301_0150
rows.name:
And, I'm really grateful that you've been giving me duties where I
might run into some decent opponents...

rows.label: qst202301_0160
rows.name: So... What's the beef exactly?

rows.label: qst202301_0170
rows.name: Well, the beef...

rows.label: qst202301_0180
rows.name: is that they're all so lame!

rows.label: qst202301_0190
rows.name:
Like, if I don't ever fight any really huge bad-ass beasts,
I can't truly express myself in battle!

rows.label: qst202301_0200
rows.name:
I need to feel that life-or-death
tension to really get my pulse going.

rows.label: qst202301_0210
rows.name:
I mean, half of the battles I wind up fighting
I could win in my sleep!

rows.label: qst202301_0220
rows.name: In other words, you're asking to fight tougher opponents?

rows.label: qst202301_0230
rows.name: Exactly!

rows.label: qst202301_0240
rows.name:
If I can't get out of this rut, my skills
are going to stagnate, atrophy.

rows.label: qst202301_0250
rows.name:
Yaegiri... I'm not sure there's enough of these
crazy bad-ass monsters to go around.

rows.label: qst202301_0260
rows.name:
Well... We have Homura and Hikari here.
I could just have a pop at them.

rows.label: qst202301_0270
rows.name: That sounds like a bad idea...

rows.label: qst202301_0280
rows.name: ...Well, yeah...

rows.label: qst202301_0290
rows.name: So why don't we go out and find some baddies to bash?

rows.label: qst202301_0300
rows.name: It's a big world!

rows.label: qst202301_0310
rows.name:
There's got to be one or two worthy opponents out there,
at the very least.

rows.label: qst202301_0320
rows.name:
Just a couple of full-blown behemoths.
Surely, we can find something?

rows.label: qst202301_0330
rows.name: I tell you, if we don't, I'm gonna explode!

rows.label: qst202301_0340
rows.name:
I might have to vent my
frustration on one of you guys!

rows.label: qst202301_0350
rows.name: Meh-meh-meh!

rows.label: qst202301_0360
rows.name: We can't have that.okay, let's look for some.

rows.label: qst202301_0370
rows.name: Roger that. It's kind of a Driver's responsibility.

rows.label: qst202301_0380
rows.name:
Yeah, I guess.
We can't have you going feral on us now, can we?

rows.label: qst202301_0390
rows.name: Hey, why don't we give her the moon on a stick?

rows.label: qst202301_0400
rows.name:
Ahahaa!
Thank you, everyone!

rows.label: qst202301_0410
rows.name: Okay! Let's get out there and get on with the hunt!
